prologue_96b53f77		"Tonight is a silent night, as I sit in front of my childhood home for the last time."	game/script.rpy	20		prologue_96b53f77
prologue_b5661fb4		"After I return from my trip, the place will have nothing but a Christmas tree and a set table."	game/script.rpy	21		prologue_b5661fb4
prologue_7aa103a8		"Tomorrow morning, I will be saying goodbye to a childhood friend who has watched my family and I grow within its walls."	game/script.rpy	23		prologue_7aa103a8
