prologue_0edeb824		"The house I grew up in isn't really a house, but no one ever asks about the two bedroom walk up I grew up in. "	game/script.rpy	27		prologue_0edeb824
prologue_bf60cc95		House is a strange word. I don't really like the way it tastes on my tongue. It feels so much more extravagant than what I live in. Why don't people ever ask about my home?	game/script.rpy	30		prologue_bf60cc95
prologue_366fde3a		"A house has enough bedrooms for every person living in the place. It has a comfy living space, a backyard and a front porch."	game/script.rpy	33		prologue_366fde3a
